msgstr "ຊື່ຂອງອຸປະກອນທີ່ຈະເຊື່ອມຕໍ່.<br/>ຕ້ອງຢູ່ໃນຮູບແບບ /dev/<device>."

#: applications/luci-app-ser2net/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/ser2net/settings.js:25
